WEBVTT

01:46.875 --> 01:48.667
PREVIOUSLY ON "DEXTER"...

01:48.667 --> 01:50.917
JESUS FUCKING CHRIST.
YOU'RE  THE BAY HARBOR BUTCHER.

01:50.917 --> 01:52.542
I REALLY HATE THAT NAME.

01:52.542 --> 01:53.917
[ BOTH GRUNTING ]

01:53.917 --> 01:55.208
[ BOTH SCREAMING ]

01:55.875 --> 01:58.333
WHAT'S IT GONNA BE, MORGAN?!

01:58.333 --> 02:00.166
KILL ME NOW
OR SET ME FREE!

02:00.166 --> 02:03.625
JAMES KNOWS THAT I BELIEVE IN
HIM, SO IT WAS WORTH THE RISK.

02:03.625 --> 02:05.583
TO YOUR JOB?
TO YOUR CAREER?

02:05.583 --> 02:08.458
WHEN YOU CARE ABOUT SOMEONE,
YOU DO WHAT YOU HAVE TO DO.

02:08.458 --> 02:10.166
AND YOUR CREDIBILITY
WAS COMPROMISED

02:10.166 --> 02:11.917
THE SECOND YOU FAILED
TO REPORT A PHONE CALL

02:11.917 --> 02:14.291
FROM THE SUBJECT
OF A GODDAMN FBI MANHUNT.

02:14.291 --> 02:17.291
WHAT REALLY PISSES ME OFF
IS YOU MIGHT BE RIGHT.

02:17.291 --> 02:20.083
THE KIDS HAVE BEEN THROUGH
SO MUCH LATELY.

02:20.083 --> 02:21.333
I DON'T WANT THEM TO FEEL

02:21.333 --> 02:24.083
LIKE THEY'VE BEEN ABANDONED
BY EVERYONE THEY LOVE.

02:24.083 --> 02:27.458
DOES THIS MEAN
WE'RE DATING AGAIN?

02:27.458 --> 02:29.041
I TRACK KILLERS.
THAT'S WHAT I DO.

02:29.041 --> 02:30.583
THEY TEND
TO MOVE AROUND.

02:30.583 --> 02:31.792
I KNOW THAT.

02:31.792 --> 02:33.458
THEN I'M NOT SURE

02:33.458 --> 02:35.792
WHAT YOU THOUGHT WOULD HAPPEN
WHEN THE CASE ENDED.

02:35.792 --> 02:37.709
I LIKE IT ROUGH.

02:37.709 --> 02:39.583
YEAH?

02:45.000 --> 02:46.208
JESUS.

02:46.208 --> 02:47.875
Dexter:
I DON'T NEED DOAKES DEAD.

02:47.875 --> 02:51.333
I JUST NEED HIS FINGERPRINTS
TO COMPLETE MY FRAME JOB.

02:51.333 --> 02:53.458
EVERY SATURDAY,
BEGINNING DIVE CLASSES

02:53.458 --> 02:56.500
PRACTICE UNDERWATER SKILLS
BESIDE THIS DOCK.

02:56.500 --> 03:00.375
TOMORROW THEY'LL FIND
A MORBID LITTLE SURPRISE.

03:00.375 --> 03:02.875
I WANT TO KNOW IF THERE WAS
ANYTHING UNUSUAL

03:02.875 --> 03:04.417
ABOUT MY FATHER'S DEATH.

03:04.417 --> 03:06.500
HE KILLED HIMSELF, DEXTER.

03:06.500 --> 03:11.458
THE IDEA OF A CODE WAS ONE
THING, BUT THE REALITY OF IT?

03:11.458 --> 03:12.542
HEY, DAD.

03:12.542 --> 03:15.125
HARRY WALKED IN
ON WHAT HE CREATED...

03:15.125 --> 03:18.333
AND HE COULDN'T LIVE
WITH HIMSELF.

03:35.875 --> 03:37.959
I ALWAYS THOUGHT
HARDENING ARTERIES

03:37.959 --> 03:39.834
SQUEEZED THE LIFE
OUT OF MY FATHER,

03:39.834 --> 03:41.875
BUT IT WAS ME.

03:45.917 --> 03:49.583
HARRY GAZED INTO THE EYES
OF HIS CREATION AND SAW EVIL,

03:49.583 --> 03:51.375
PURE AND SIMPLE.

03:51.375 --> 03:54.041
MY EVIL --
IT KILLED HIM.

03:54.041 --> 03:58.041
Doakes: THAT SHIT
ABOUT YOUR FATHER --

03:58.041 --> 04:01.375
IF YOU WANT TO
TALK ABOUT IT...

04:01.375 --> 04:02.500
ABOUT WHAT?

04:02.500 --> 04:06.709
THAT MY LIFE
IS ONE TRAGIC MISTAKE?

04:06.709 --> 04:09.792
WE'VE ALL FELT THAT AT ONE TIME
OR ANOTHER. I KNOW I HAVE.

04:09.792 --> 04:12.417
DID YOU HAPPEN TO BE STUFFING
A HUMAN LEG INTO A GARBAGE BAG

04:12.417 --> 04:13.667
AT THAT POINT?

04:13.667 --> 04:16.208
IF YOU WANT TO MAKE A CHANGE,
MORGAN, NOW'S THE TIME.

04:16.208 --> 04:18.834
ALL YOU GOT TO DO
IS LET ME OUT OF HERE.

04:18.834 --> 04:20.750
IT'S OVER, MAN.

04:20.750 --> 04:23.709
IT IS OVER
WHEN I SAY IT IS!

04:23.709 --> 04:25.583
THERE'S THAT ANGER
AGAIN.

04:25.583 --> 04:27.709
YOU GOT TO LET THAT OUT,
MAN.

04:27.709 --> 04:30.375
CAREFUL, SERGEANT,
YOU MIGHT GET YOUR WISH.

04:32.625 --> 04:35.166
I'M FLYING
WITHOUT A CODE HERE.

04:35.166 --> 04:37.792
I CAN UNLEASH THE BEAST
ANYTIME I WANT.

04:37.792 --> 04:39.917
MORGAN, YOU KNOW
THAT'S NOT THE ANSWER.

04:39.917 --> 04:41.583
BUT IT WOULD FEEL
FUCKING GREAT.

04:41.583 --> 04:44.750
BUT YOU WOULD HATE YOURSELF
FOR THE REST OF YOUR LIFE.

04:55.041 --> 05:00.917
ALL THE THINGS HARRY TAUGHT ME,
EVERYTHING --

05:00.917 --> 05:04.000
IT'S BULLSHIT.

05:07.542 --> 05:10.458
IT'S THE ONLY WAY
I KNOW HOW TO LIVE.

05:10.458 --> 05:14.125
TURN YOURSELF IN.

05:14.125 --> 05:16.125
[ SCOFFS ]

05:16.125 --> 05:19.125
RULE NUMBER ONE --

05:19.125 --> 05:22.083
DON'T GET CAUGHT.

05:22.083 --> 05:24.583
NO, NO, MORGAN,
YOU'RE SPINNING.

05:24.583 --> 05:25.834
LET ME HELP YOU.

05:25.834 --> 05:28.291
IT'S ONLY A MATTER OF TIME
BEFORE YOU HURT SOMEONE ELSE.

05:28.291 --> 05:29.583
AND I'M NOT TALKING
ABOUT ME --

05:29.583 --> 05:31.500
I'M TALKING ABOUT YOUR SISTER
OR YOUR GIRLFRIEND

05:31.500 --> 05:34.375
OR EVEN THOSE KIDS.

05:34.375 --> 05:35.542
I WOULD NEVER --

05:35.542 --> 05:37.417
NO, NOT ON PURPOSE,
BUT YOU CAN'T CONTROL THAT SHIT

05:37.417 --> 05:38.917
THAT'S GROWING
INSIDE OF YOU, MORGAN.

05:38.917 --> 05:40.000
IT'S LIKE CANCER.

05:40.000 --> 05:45.041
AND IN CASE YOU HAVEN'T NOTICED,
IT'S SPREADING.

05:45.041 --> 05:46.875
END IT NOW.

05:46.875 --> 05:52.208
TAKE RESPONSIBILITY
FOR WHO YOU ARE, MAN.

05:52.208 --> 05:53.834
WE'LL GO
TO THE STATION TOGETHER.

05:53.834 --> 05:55.542
I'LL HELP YOU.

06:00.542 --> 06:03.125
[ CELLPHONE RINGS ]

06:04.166 --> 06:05.834
MORGAN.

06:05.834 --> 06:07.834
MORGAN,
DON'T ANSWER THAT.

06:07.834 --> 06:11.458
STAY WITH ME, MAN.

06:11.458 --> 06:12.917
MORGAN!

06:12.917 --> 06:14.500
MORGAN!

06:14.500 --> 06:17.208
FUCK!

06:17.208 --> 06:18.875
YES,
THIS IS DEXTER MORGAN.

06:18.875 --> 06:20.625
Mr. Morgan,
my name is Dr. Hill.

06:20.625 --> 06:22.583
I work at
Good Samaritan Hospital.

06:22.583 --> 06:25.166
I'm calling
on behalf of Lila Tournay.

06:25.166 --> 06:26.709
HOW DID YOU
GET THIS NUMBER?

06:26.709 --> 06:29.542
You're listed
as her emergency contact.

06:29.542 --> 06:31.959
Ms. Tournay was rushed
into our E.R.

06:31.959 --> 06:33.083
IN RESPIRATORY ARREST.

06:33.083 --> 06:34.625
COULD YOU COME TO
THE HOSPITAL?

06:34.625 --> 06:36.667
I'M TWO HOURS AWAY.
CALL SOMEBODY ELSE.

06:36.667 --> 06:40.000
Mr. Morgan,
there's a legal complication.

06:40.000 --> 06:43.250
WHAT KIND OF COMPLICATION?

06:43.250 --> 06:45.417
I can't discuss it
over the phone.

06:45.417 --> 06:48.041
You really need
to be here.

06:48.041 --> 06:49.041
[ EXHALES SHARPLY ]

06:52.125 --> 06:53.709
WHERE ARE YOU GOING,
MORGAN?

06:53.709 --> 06:55.709
DON'T WORRY, I'LL SEND
THE FBI YOUR WAY SOON ENOUGH.

06:55.709 --> 06:57.834
YOU'RE STILL
GONNA TRY TO FRAME ME?

06:57.834 --> 07:01.125
I'M KIND OF
DOWN A PATH HERE.

07:01.125 --> 07:03.417
YOU'LL GET YOUR CHANCE
TO TELL THEM I'M THE KILLER,

07:03.417 --> 07:05.959
AND THEY'LL IGNORE YOU
LIKE BEFORE, AND I'LL --

07:05.959 --> 07:07.417
AND YOU'LL BURN IN HELL.

07:07.417 --> 07:09.417
SOMETHING LIKE THAT.

07:10.500 --> 07:12.208
Doakes: MORGAN!

07:12.208 --> 07:15.083
[ DOOR LOCKS ]

07:15.083 --> 07:16.959
[ CAR DOOR CLOSES ]

07:16.959 --> 07:18.792
[ ENGINE TURNS OVER ]

07:58.792 --> 08:00.875
HE'S GONE, DEX.
[ SNIFFLES ]

08:00.875 --> 08:03.083
DAD'S HEART
FINALLY GAVE OUT.

08:08.000 --> 08:11.166
HARRY'S HEART GAVE OUT
WHEN HE SAW WHAT'S INSIDE ME.

08:11.166 --> 08:13.709
HE THOUGHT HE COULD TAME IT,
GIVE IT A PURPOSE,

08:13.709 --> 08:15.959
HELP IT FIND A PLACE
IN THE NATURAL ORDER.

08:15.959 --> 08:19.083
GUESS HE WAS WRONG.

08:21.917 --> 08:23.667
DEXTER?

08:23.667 --> 08:25.333
MR. MORGAN?
YEAH.

08:25.333 --> 08:28.500
I NEED A SECOND ALONE
WITH HIM, OKAY? THANKS.

08:28.500 --> 08:30.333
DR. HILL --
WE SPOKE ON THE PHONE

08:30.333 --> 08:32.375
REGARDING YOUR GIRLFRIEND,
MS. TOURNAY.

08:32.375 --> 08:34.125
SHE'S NOT
MY GIRLFRIEND.

08:34.125 --> 08:36.333
OH, I THOUGHT
SHE SAID SHE WAS.

08:36.333 --> 08:38.208
YEAH,
SHE PROBABLY DID.

08:38.208 --> 08:39.166
SO, YOU'RE...

08:39.166 --> 08:40.625
IT'S COMPLICATED.

08:40.625 --> 08:42.500
LOOK,
WHY IS ANGEL HERE?

08:42.500 --> 08:45.959
WE FOUND ROHYPNOL,
THE DATE-RAPE DRUG,

08:45.959 --> 08:47.125
IN LILA'S SYSTEM.

08:47.125 --> 08:50.250
WITH HER BRUISING, THE WOUND
TO THE BACK OF HER HEAD --

08:50.250 --> 08:53.166
WE MAY BE LOOKING AT A CASE
OF SEXUAL ASSAULT.

08:53.166 --> 08:54.792
NO, NO,
THAT DIDN'T HAPPEN.

08:54.792 --> 08:58.000
MS. TOURNAY HAS NO RECOLLECTION
OF WHAT DID  HAPPEN.

08:58.000 --> 09:00.458
SHE'S REQUESTED
WE PERFORM A RAPE KIT.

09:00.458 --> 09:01.667
[ SIGHS ]

09:01.667 --> 09:03.834
I NEED TO TALK TO HER.

09:19.083 --> 09:21.542
DEXTER,
YOU CAME TO SEE ME.

09:21.542 --> 09:23.542
YOU'RE SO SWEET.

09:23.542 --> 09:27.709
THE DOCTORS THINK
ANGEL RAPED YOU.

09:30.542 --> 09:33.041
DID HE?
EVERYTHING'S A BIT FUZZY.

09:33.041 --> 09:35.000
THIS IS DESPERATE.

09:35.000 --> 09:36.375
IT WON'T WORK.

09:36.375 --> 09:39.375
WHAT ARE YOU
TALKING ABOUT?

09:39.375 --> 09:42.000
I'M JUST GLAD
YOU'RE HERE.

09:42.000 --> 09:45.125
I MISSED YOU SO MUCH.

09:45.125 --> 09:47.709
THIS IS HOW
YOU WIN ME BACK?

09:47.709 --> 09:50.709
FRAMING A GOOD MAN
TO GET WHAT YOU WANT?

09:50.709 --> 09:53.875
WHICH IS PRECISELY
WHAT I'M DOING TO DOAKES.

09:56.250 --> 09:59.166
WHAT'S THE MATTER,
DEXTER?

09:59.166 --> 10:01.750
YOU LOOK SO SAD...LOST.

10:04.417 --> 10:07.583
DON'T DO THIS.

10:07.583 --> 10:10.250
I WON'T PRESS CHARGES
AGAINST ANGEL.

10:10.250 --> 10:13.750
I'LL DO
WHATEVER YOU WANT.

10:16.542 --> 10:19.750
IF YOU PROMISE
TO TAKE ME BACK.

10:19.750 --> 10:21.917
WHY CAN'T YOU
JUST LET ME GO?

10:21.917 --> 10:25.750
BECAUSE I'M
YOUR REAL SOUL MATE.

10:25.750 --> 10:27.917
NOT RITA.

10:27.917 --> 10:29.125
ME.

10:29.125 --> 10:31.125
I SEE YOU.

10:31.125 --> 10:33.583
INSIDE.

10:34.792 --> 10:36.375
I'M THE ONLY ONE.

10:36.375 --> 10:39.166
LOOK WHERE
IT'S GOTTEN YOU.

10:41.333 --> 10:43.166
[ DOOR OPENS, CLOSES ]

10:44.792 --> 10:47.291
YOU KNOW THAT I COULD NEVER
DO ANYTHING LIKE THAT, RIGHT?

10:47.291 --> 10:49.917
YOU DON'T EVEN HAVE
TO SAY ANYTHING, ANGEL.

10:49.917 --> 10:54.000
YOU WARNED ME ABOUT HER,
BUT MY DICK WOULDN'T LISTEN.

10:54.000 --> 10:57.125
I COULD LOSE EVERYTHING
OVER THIS.

10:57.125 --> 11:00.208
WHAT WOULD I SAY
TO MY LITTLE GIRL?

11:00.208 --> 11:02.959
THE DOCTOR SAID LILA
HAS 72 HOURS TO PRESS CHARGES.

11:02.959 --> 11:04.834
MAYBE SHE'LL COME
TO HER SENSES.

11:04.834 --> 11:06.750
[ SIGHS ]

11:08.834 --> 11:11.125
I SHOULD GET HOME AND GRAB
A FEW HOURS OF SLEEP.

11:11.125 --> 11:12.333
LET ME GET THIS.

11:12.333 --> 11:14.667
NO, BACK OFF.
I GOT IT.

11:19.166 --> 11:21.291
OH, ANGEL.

11:23.792 --> 11:26.041
IF I GOT
TO CHOOSE A PERSON --

11:26.041 --> 11:31.500
A REAL PERSON --
TO BE LIKE...

11:31.500 --> 11:33.458
OUT OF ANYONE,
IT'D BE YOU.

11:35.834 --> 11:40.166
I'M NOT REALLY SURE WHAT
THAT MEANS, BUT, THANKS, DEX.

11:44.834 --> 11:48.917
SEE YOU
IN THE MORNING.

11:48.917 --> 11:52.375
OH, AND, UH,
I'D APPRECIATE IT

11:52.375 --> 11:56.250
IF YOU DIDN'T MENTION THIS
TO ANYONE AT THE STATION.

11:56.250 --> 11:58.041
OF COURSE NOT.

11:58.041 --> 12:00.000
THANKS.

12:02.875 --> 12:04.000
HOW DID IT COME TO THIS?

12:04.000 --> 12:05.709
I'VE ALWAYS GONE
AFTER CRIMINALS.

12:05.709 --> 12:08.834
NOW I HAVE THE FATE
OF TWO COPS IN MY HANDS.

12:08.834 --> 12:10.500
DOAKES WAS RIGHT.

12:10.500 --> 12:12.667
THE CANCER IS SPREADING.

12:18.542 --> 12:19.625
WE'RE OUT OF YOGURT.

12:19.625 --> 12:21.375
Lundy:
ADD IT TO THE LIST.

12:21.375 --> 12:23.125
WE'LL STOP
BY THE STORE TONIGHT.

12:23.125 --> 12:25.041
THE STORE'S
ON THE WAY TO WORK.

12:25.041 --> 12:26.542
IT'S ALSO
ON THE WAY HOME.

12:26.542 --> 12:27.875
WE'RE GONNA BE LATE.

12:27.875 --> 12:30.375
HEY, WHO JOINED WHO
IN THE SHOWER THIS MORNING?

12:30.375 --> 12:31.834
HOW ABOUT,
IN THE FUTURE,

12:31.834 --> 12:33.583
I SET THE ALARM
10 MINUTES EARLIER?

12:33.583 --> 12:36.083
MAKE IT 20.

12:36.083 --> 12:38.458
"THE FUTURE --"
I'M LIKING THE SOUND OF THAT.

12:38.458 --> 12:40.959
[ CELLPHONE RINGS ]

12:43.709 --> 12:45.583
WE'RE BEING ORDERED
TO WORK.

12:45.583 --> 12:48.417
FUCK THAT. YOU'RE THE HEAD
OF THE TASK FORCE.

12:48.417 --> 12:49.458
YOU DO THE ORDERING.

12:49.458 --> 12:51.583
[ CELLPHONE RINGS ]

12:53.709 --> 12:55.750
WHO'S D.D. ADAMS?

12:55.750 --> 12:57.875
MY BOSS.

13:00.417 --> 13:02.458
MISSION ACCOMPLISHED.

13:02.458 --> 13:04.125
THE WEAPONS
I TOSSED INTO THE OCEAN

13:04.125 --> 13:05.583
WERE FOUND AS PLANNED.

13:05.583 --> 13:07.667
ONE MORE NAIL
IN DOAKES' COFFIN.

13:07.667 --> 13:09.458
ALL RIGHT, PEOPLE.
LISTEN UP.

13:09.458 --> 13:11.709
THIS IS FBI DEPUTY DIRECTOR
MAX ADAMS.

13:11.709 --> 13:13.625
HE JUST GOT IN
FROM WASHINGTON.

13:13.625 --> 13:15.792
HE'S GOING TO BE
HELPING US OUT FOR A WHILE.

13:15.792 --> 13:17.625
MAX.

13:17.625 --> 13:19.417
FRANK.

13:19.417 --> 13:22.500
ONCE AGAIN, I HAVE PLEDGED OUR
FULL COOPERATION AND RESOURCES,

13:22.500 --> 13:25.208
SO LET'S MAKE HIM
FEEL AT HOME.

13:25.208 --> 13:26.625
MAX.

13:26.625 --> 13:29.667
THE MURDER WEAPONS BEFORE YOU
WERE RECOVERED YESTERDAY

13:29.667 --> 13:32.458
BY A BEGINNING
SCUBA-DIVING CLASS.

13:32.458 --> 13:34.792
THE INSTRUCTOR
CONTACTED THE FBI DIRECTLY,

13:34.792 --> 13:36.083
WHICH BROUGHT THEM
TO MY ATTENTION.

13:36.083 --> 13:39.291
FINGERPRINT ANALYSIS
TIES THEM TO ONE JAMES DOAKES.

13:39.291 --> 13:40.792
THIS DOESN'T
PROVE A GODDAMN THING.

13:40.792 --> 13:41.750
Not now, Maria.

13:41.750 --> 13:43.375
WHY I WASN'T
I BROUGHT IN ON THIS?

13:43.375 --> 13:45.667
YOU JUST WERE, FRANK.

13:45.667 --> 13:46.792
NOW, WE KNOW SERGEANT DOAKES
HAS BEEN...

13:46.792 --> 13:48.917
Lundy better
watch his back.

13:48.917 --> 13:50.667
...HE'S ABANDONED
THE TOOLS OF THE TRADE,

13:50.667 --> 13:52.750
THAT MEANS
HE'S PROBABLY ON THE RUN.

13:52.750 --> 13:55.458
THIS FOOTAGE WAS TAKEN
FOUR DAYS AGO AT A MOBIL STATION

13:55.458 --> 13:58.875
JUST OFF HIGHWAY 41,
SOUTHEAST OF NAPLES.

13:58.875 --> 14:03.500
LADIES AND GENTLEMEN,
SERGEANT JAMES DOAKES.

14:03.500 --> 14:06.583
I CAN'T BELIEVE IT.

14:06.583 --> 14:09.208
$3.49 FOR REGULAR?

14:09.208 --> 14:15.166
SO, WE  HAVE LET OUR TARGET
GET AWAY ONCE.

14:15.166 --> 14:17.792
LET'S NOT DROP THE BALL AGAIN.

14:17.792 --> 14:19.166
Asshole.

14:19.166 --> 14:22.542
HIGHWAY 41 RUNS THROUGH
THE EVERGLADES NATIONAL PARK.

14:22.542 --> 14:23.667
IT WON'T BE LONG NOW.

14:23.667 --> 14:25.709
I CAN HANG THIS ON DOAKES
AND THEN...

14:28.583 --> 14:30.125
THEN WHAT?

14:30.125 --> 14:32.792
YEARS OF TRIALS AND APPEALS
WITH HIM POINTING HIS FINGER

14:32.792 --> 14:35.041
AND CALLING ME KILLER?

14:35.041 --> 14:40.750
FOR SUCH A NEAT MONSTER,
I'M MAKING AN AWFULLY BIG MESS.

14:40.750 --> 14:42.875
[ CLANGING ]

15:23.333 --> 15:25.417
WHERE DOES
THIS PRICK ADAMS

15:25.417 --> 15:28.250
GET OFF TAKING
SUCH CHEAP SHOTS AT LUNDY?

15:28.250 --> 15:29.917
I HEARD THAT
DOAKES WALKED OFF

15:29.917 --> 15:31.792
IN THE MIDDLE OF
LUNDY'S QUESTIONING

15:31.792 --> 15:33.125
AND THAT LUNDY
DIDN'T STOP HIM.

15:35.375 --> 15:37.583
I MIGHT HAVE
HEARD THAT WRONG.

15:37.583 --> 15:38.917
Peters: MORGAN.

15:38.917 --> 15:40.625
PETERS.

15:40.625 --> 15:41.875
NICE HAIR, BORELLI.

15:41.875 --> 15:43.417
I'M SURE THE JOHNS
UP IN BOYS TOWN

15:43.417 --> 15:45.583
ARE LOVING THAT
DURAN DURAN LOOK.

15:45.583 --> 15:47.166
WHAT'S THE MATTER?

15:47.166 --> 15:49.083
YOU MEATHEADS
LOSE YOUR SENSE OF HUMOR?

15:49.083 --> 15:51.000
YOUR JOKE WASN'T FUNNY.

15:51.000 --> 15:53.750
WE HAVE A WARRANT FOR
DETECTIVE BATISTA'S ARREST.

15:57.750 --> 16:00.750
BULLSHIT. FOR WHAT?

16:00.750 --> 16:02.625
A WOMAN NAMED
LILA TOURNAY

16:02.625 --> 16:05.291
HAS FILED SEXUAL-ASSAULT
CHARGES AGAINST HIM.

16:05.291 --> 16:06.333
THAT FUCKING BITCH.

16:06.333 --> 16:08.959
DEBRA, IT'S OKAY.
I KNEW THIS WAS COMING.

16:08.959 --> 16:11.000
IT'S NOT OKAY.
CAPTAIN, LIEUTENANT!

16:11.000 --> 16:13.709
PUT THOSE AWAY OR I WILL
SHOVE THEM UP YOUR ASS!

16:13.709 --> 16:15.250
LaGuerta:
WHAT'S GOING ON HERE?

16:15.250 --> 16:18.291
Borelli:
WE'VE BEEN ASKED TO BRING
DETECTIVE BATISTA UPSTAIRS.

16:18.291 --> 16:19.959
I AM SURE
THAT DETECTIVE BATISTA

16:19.959 --> 16:21.917
WILL GO ALONG
WITH YOU PEACEFULLY.

16:21.917 --> 16:25.375
VAMOS DESPUéS.

16:25.375 --> 16:27.792
IT'S NOT YOUR FAULT.

16:27.792 --> 16:30.792
I'LL BE OKAY.

16:30.792 --> 16:32.333
IT ISN'T MY FAULT.

16:32.333 --> 16:34.208
I WARNED ANGEL.

16:34.208 --> 16:37.750
STILL, I HATE TO SEE HIM
DISGRACED IN FRONT OF EVERYONE.

16:39.709 --> 16:45.583
AND LaGUERTA ABOUT TO LOSE HER
FORMER PARTNER, HER FRIEND.

16:45.583 --> 16:48.083
EVEN LUNDY IS CAUGHT

16:48.083 --> 16:50.166
IN HURRICANE DEXTER'S
PATH OF DESTRUCTION.

16:52.750 --> 16:55.000
MAYBE THIS IS HOW EVIL WORKS.

16:55.000 --> 17:00.542
DESTROYING EVERYTHING IT
TOUCHES...INCLUDING MY FATHER.

17:00.542 --> 17:04.208
[ CELLPHONE RINGS ]

17:04.208 --> 17:05.792
HEY.

17:05.792 --> 17:08.875
YOU'RE NOT GONNA BELIEVE
THE MORNING I'M HAVING.

17:08.875 --> 17:10.250
I KNOW THE FEELING.

17:10.250 --> 17:12.667
My car is stalled
on Harper and 3rd.

17:12.667 --> 17:15.166
THINK YOU CAN
COME GET ME?

17:15.166 --> 17:16.834
YEAH, HANG TIGHT.
I'LL BE RIGHT THERE.

17:16.834 --> 17:18.625
Thanks, Dex.

17:20.250 --> 17:23.709
I'M THE HELPFUL HANDYMAN.
HOW EVIL CAN I POSSIBLY BE?

17:23.709 --> 17:27.375
I'M SPARING RITA AND DEB
BY FRAMING DOAKES.

17:27.375 --> 17:28.542
RIGHT?

17:30.417 --> 17:32.417
[ PANTING ]

17:42.792 --> 17:44.417
[ GROWLING ]

17:53.208 --> 17:55.917
[ GROWLING CONTINUES ]

18:06.291 --> 18:08.208
[ PANTING ]

18:10.083 --> 18:12.208
[ ENGINE WHIRRING ]

18:25.375 --> 18:26.750
HEY! HEY!

18:26.750 --> 18:27.792
OVER HERE!

18:34.750 --> 18:36.458
THANK GOD.

18:36.458 --> 18:37.917
EH, PANA.
QUE HACES POR AQUí.

18:37.917 --> 18:41.458
I'VE BEEN HELD PRISONER IN
A CABIN FOR TWO FUCKING DAYS.

18:41.458 --> 18:43.417
CABAÑA?
SI, SI, LA CABAÑA.

18:43.417 --> 18:44.583
FUCKING HELLHOLE.

18:44.583 --> 18:45.917
[ SPEAKING SPANISH ]

18:45.917 --> 18:47.834
CUAL ES LA CABAÑA?

18:47.834 --> 18:49.583
NO, NO. I DON'T WANT
TO GO TO THE CABIN.

18:49.583 --> 18:51.333
LA CABAÑA ESTA ALLá.

18:52.166 --> 18:53.834
I NEED YOU TO GET MY ASS
OUT OF HERE.

18:53.834 --> 18:55.750
I'M A POLICE SERGEANT.
MIAMI METRO HOMICIDE.

18:55.750 --> 18:56.667
POLICIA?

18:56.667 --> 18:58.583
SI, SI. POLICIA.

18:58.583 --> 19:00.625
[ GRUNTS ]

19:00.625 --> 19:02.333
VAMANOS.

19:02.333 --> 19:05.166
[ ENGINE TURNS OVER ]

19:08.959 --> 19:10.333
I'VE GOT
TO RUN UPSTAIRS.

19:10.333 --> 19:12.208
THERE'S A WHOLE
BATISTA THING GOING ON.

19:12.208 --> 19:14.000
LUNCH TODAY?
DOUBTFUL.

19:14.000 --> 19:16.417
I'VE GOT TO WRITE UP
A STATUS REPORT

19:16.417 --> 19:18.041
FOR DEPUTY DIRECTOR ADAMS.

19:18.041 --> 19:19.792
WHY'D THEY SEND
THAT DIPSHIT?

19:19.792 --> 19:22.583
WASHINGTON GETS NERVOUS WHEN
THERE'S NO MOVEMENT ON A CASE,

19:22.583 --> 19:23.792
ESPECIALLY ONE
AS BIG AS THIS.

19:23.792 --> 19:25.000
NO MOVEMENT?

19:25.000 --> 19:28.125
YOU'RE THE REASON THEY FOUND
THE BLOOD SLIDES IN DOAKES' CAR.

19:28.125 --> 19:31.000
I'M ALSO THE ONE
WHO LET HIM GET AWAY.

19:31.000 --> 19:33.041
WE ALL LET HIM
GET AWAY.

19:33.041 --> 19:34.417
I WAS IN CHARGE.

19:34.417 --> 19:37.000
THE EVIDENCE WAS THERE,

19:37.000 --> 19:39.333
BUT SOMETHING INSIDE ME
WASN'T CONVINCED HE WAS OUR GUY,

19:39.333 --> 19:41.583
SO I LET HIM WALK.

19:41.583 --> 19:43.875
IT WAS A BAD CALL.

19:43.875 --> 19:45.291
NOW WE MIGHT NEVER --

19:45.291 --> 19:46.542
STOP IT.

19:46.542 --> 19:47.917
STOP WHAT?

19:47.917 --> 19:51.083
ACTING LIKE ME.

19:51.083 --> 19:52.667
YOU'RE A GOD.

19:52.667 --> 19:55.208
DON'T YOU FORGET IT.

19:57.166 --> 20:00.500
Rita:
SO, WHAT DO YOU THINK IT IS?

20:00.500 --> 20:01.709
CARBURETOR.

20:01.709 --> 20:03.000
TRANSMISSION.

20:03.000 --> 20:05.709
THAT ROUND, BLACK
HOSE THING.

20:05.709 --> 20:07.500
[ SIGHS ]
I'M MORE A BOAT GUY.

20:07.500 --> 20:10.792
THE LAST THING I NEED RIGHT NOW
IS A MAJOR REPAIR BILL.

20:10.792 --> 20:13.041
THROW IN A TOW
AND RENTAL CAR,

20:13.041 --> 20:15.792
THERE GOES ASTOR'S
PIANO LESSONS.

20:15.792 --> 20:17.375
HERE, TAKE THE MINI-VAN.

20:17.375 --> 20:19.959
NO, I CAN'T. IT'S TOO
BIG OF AN INCONVENIENCE.

20:19.959 --> 20:21.500
YOU CAN DROP ME OFF
BACK AT WORK.

20:21.500 --> 20:24.375
I'LL BORROW SOMETHING
FROM THE MOTOR POOL.

20:26.709 --> 20:29.542
I'LL MAKE IT UP TO YOU.

20:29.542 --> 20:31.792
DINNER?

20:31.792 --> 20:34.125
I HAVE A BETTER IDEA.

20:34.125 --> 20:36.125
PACK A LUNCH,
BRING THE KIDS,

20:36.125 --> 20:38.375
LET ME TAKE YOU
OUT ON THE OCEAN TOMORROW.

20:38.375 --> 20:40.125
THE KIDS
HAVE SCHOOL TOMORROW.

20:40.125 --> 20:41.917
THINK OF IT
AS A FIELD TRIP.

20:41.917 --> 20:43.750
[ CHUCKLES ]
YOU DON'T KNOW CODY'S TEACHER.

20:43.750 --> 20:47.166
IT'S JUST ONE DAY --
JUST ONE MORE DAY.

20:48.500 --> 20:50.583
IS EVERYTHING OKAY,
DEXTER?

20:50.583 --> 20:53.000
LOOK, AFTER EVERYTHING
WE'VE BEEN THROUGH LATELY,

20:53.000 --> 20:56.250
I JUST WANT TO BE TOGETHER
WITH YOU GUYS.

20:56.250 --> 20:58.041
IS THAT SELFISH?

20:58.041 --> 21:00.750
NO.

21:00.750 --> 21:03.041
NO, IT'S LOVELY.

21:11.917 --> 21:14.166
SERGEANT DOAKES CAN REJOICE.

21:14.166 --> 21:16.625
I COME BEARING REAL FOOD.

21:31.166 --> 21:33.125
Shit.

21:33.125 --> 21:34.792
[ MAN SPEAKING SPANISH ]

21:41.208 --> 21:43.041
APURATE. ALLí.

21:43.041 --> 21:45.417
[ SPEAKING SPANISH ]

22:15.291 --> 22:17.458
[ SPEAKING SPANISH ]

22:23.041 --> 22:25.000
HEY, VAMANOS.

22:25.000 --> 22:27.166
NO, NO, NO.
[ SPEAKING SPANISH ]

22:30.375 --> 22:32.625
SUCK MY DICK, MOTHERFUCKER.
YOU UNDERSTAND THAT SHIT? HUH?

22:32.625 --> 22:34.083
APURATE.

22:34.083 --> 22:35.834
[ CLATTERING ]
ESTEBAN?

22:35.834 --> 22:36.917
ESTEBAN!

22:36.917 --> 22:39.625
ESTEBAN, VAMANOS.

22:39.625 --> 22:41.458
[ BOTH SPEAKING SPANISH ]

22:43.166 --> 22:44.959
GABRóN NO MEJOR
A VENTELLAR.

22:46.500 --> 22:48.542
ESTEBAN!
[ SPEAKING SPANISH ]

22:49.834 --> 22:51.542
ESTEBAN?

22:53.667 --> 22:55.542
AAH!

22:58.583 --> 23:00.500
[ PANTING ]

23:04.875 --> 23:06.375
FRIENDS OF YOURS?

23:06.375 --> 23:07.750
FROM WHAT I CAN TELL,

23:07.750 --> 23:10.000
THEY'RE FRIENDS
OF THAT DRUG DEALER.

23:10.000 --> 23:11.625
THEY WOULD'VE KILLED ME

23:11.625 --> 23:14.542
ONCE I HAD ALL THAT COKE
ON THE BOAT.

23:14.542 --> 23:15.875
[ SIGHS ]

23:15.875 --> 23:17.542
THANKS, MORGAN.

23:22.917 --> 23:27.166
WELL, THIS IS AWKWARD.

23:30.208 --> 23:32.542
I THINK WE MADE
SOME ALLIGATORS VERY HAPPY.

23:36.500 --> 23:38.291
SO, HERE WE ARE.

23:38.291 --> 23:41.709
BACK TO FUCKING
SQUARE ONE.

23:41.709 --> 23:43.083
NOT EXACTLY.

23:49.417 --> 23:51.625
I'LL TELL YOU WHAT,
JAMES.

23:51.625 --> 23:53.458
CAN I CALL YOU JAMES?

23:53.458 --> 23:55.375
KNOCK YOURSELF OUT.

23:59.166 --> 24:01.375
I'M TOYING
WITH AN IDEA.

24:04.083 --> 24:09.000
I'VE BEEN UNDER FEDERAL
INVESTIGATION FOR TWO MONTHS.

24:09.000 --> 24:11.375
MY TROPHIES WERE STOLEN.

24:12.875 --> 24:14.875
SORRY.

24:14.875 --> 24:20.208
THE CODE I LIVE BY
HAS BEEN SHATTERED.

24:20.208 --> 24:22.500
AND I HAVE A CO-WORKER
IN A CAGE.

24:22.500 --> 24:24.333
THINGS AREN'T
GOING SO WELL.

24:24.333 --> 24:25.458
[ SCOFFS ]

24:25.458 --> 24:27.959
NO SHIT.
I CAN SEE THAT.

24:27.959 --> 24:33.709
YOU TOLD ME, "TAKE
RESPONSIBILITY FOR WHAT I AM."

24:33.709 --> 24:35.500
YOU WERE RIGHT.

24:38.375 --> 24:40.875
HARRY KILLED
THE WRONG PERSON.

24:40.875 --> 24:42.375
MORGAN, YOU'RE NOT
THINKING ABOUT --

24:42.375 --> 24:45.500
KILL MYSELF?
NO, THAT'S PATHETIC.

24:48.417 --> 24:52.291
BUT I CAN'T LIVE IN THIS
HOUSE OF CARDS ANYMORE,

24:52.291 --> 24:54.750
WAITING FOR IT
ALL TO FALL DOWN.

24:54.750 --> 24:57.625
I NEED TO DO SOMETHING,
YOU KNOW?

24:57.625 --> 24:59.917
[ SIGHS ]

25:05.375 --> 25:08.375
I'M THINKING ABOUT
TURNING MYSELF IN.

25:13.542 --> 25:17.125
THAT'S A --
THAT'S A GOOD CALL, MORGAN.

25:17.125 --> 25:19.250
THAT'S A TOUGH CALL,

25:19.250 --> 25:21.291
BUT...
THAT'S A GOOD CALL, MAN.

25:25.750 --> 25:28.333
I NEED SOME
FUCKING RELIEF.

25:28.333 --> 25:31.166
YEAH, YOU CAN'T
KEEP RUNNING, MAN.

25:31.166 --> 25:32.625
THAT'S FOR PUSSIES.

25:32.625 --> 25:36.083
YOU'RE JUST GONNA END UP
IN EXACTLY THE SAME SITUATION

25:36.083 --> 25:36.959
SOONER OR LATER.

25:36.959 --> 25:38.500
PRISON.

25:41.083 --> 25:44.333
I COULD FINALLY
GET SOME SLEEP.

25:45.417 --> 25:46.834
YEAH.

25:48.542 --> 25:53.792
IN THE LONG RUN
WOULD BE EASIER ON DEB...

25:53.792 --> 25:55.667
RITA.

25:58.750 --> 26:03.750
BETTER THAN WATCHING ME
DRAGGED IN LIKE AN ANIMAL...

26:03.750 --> 26:07.625
WHICH, LET'S FACE IT,
WILL HAPPEN, SOMEDAY.

26:07.625 --> 26:08.750
YEAH.

26:08.750 --> 26:11.875
MORGAN,
WE'LL DO IT TOGETHER.

26:11.875 --> 26:13.500
I'LL GO WITH YOU.

26:13.500 --> 26:15.375
COME ON, LET'S GO.

26:17.208 --> 26:20.375
IF I DO THIS, I NEED A DAY
TO GET MY AFFAIRS IN ORDER.

26:20.375 --> 26:22.792
THAT'S FINE. TIE ME UP,
THROW ME IN THE TRUNK.
COME ON, LET'S GO.

26:22.792 --> 26:25.417
I BROUGHT SUPPLIES.
FRESH FRUIT.

26:25.417 --> 26:27.250
MAKE SURE
YOU MENTION THAT

26:27.250 --> 26:29.333
WHEN THEY INTERVIEW YOU
FOR THE STORY OF MY LIFE.

26:29.333 --> 26:32.208
GOD DAMN IT, YOU'RE NOT GONNA
LEAVE ME IN THIS CAGE --
ANYTHING COULD HAPPEN.

26:32.208 --> 26:33.417
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

26:33.417 --> 26:36.583
I THINK WE'VE SEEN
THE WORST OF THAT.

26:36.583 --> 26:38.375
MORGAN!

26:38.375 --> 26:41.542
DEXTER.

26:43.709 --> 26:47.208
I'VE REALLY ENJOYED
OUR CONVERSATIONS, JAMES.

26:50.083 --> 26:54.542
I LIE
TO EVERYONE I KNOW...

26:54.542 --> 26:58.667
EXCEPT MY VICTIMS
RIGHT BEFORE I KILL THEM.

26:58.667 --> 27:02.750
IT'S HARD TO ESTABLISH
MUCH OF A RAPPORT THERE.

27:09.291 --> 27:11.667
SORRY ABOUT THE CAGE.

27:13.458 --> 27:14.959
MORGAN!

27:14.959 --> 27:17.041
[ DOOR OPENS ]

27:17.041 --> 27:18.166
FUCK.

27:45.083 --> 27:47.834
[ DIALING ]

27:47.834 --> 27:49.709
[ CELLPHONE RINGING ]

27:54.959 --> 27:56.166
Debra: What?

27:56.166 --> 27:58.041
HEY, DEB. IT'S ME.
WHAT ARE YOU DOING TONIGHT?

27:58.041 --> 28:01.083
I'M ABOUT TO GET
OFF OF WORK, WHY?

28:01.083 --> 28:04.875
I'VE GOT SOME PAPERS
I NEED YOU TO SIGN.

28:04.875 --> 28:06.792
PAPERS?
WHAT KIND OF PAPERS?

28:08.875 --> 28:10.959
I'LL EXPLAIN
WHEN I SEE YOU.

28:10.959 --> 28:13.000
Well, I'm meeting Masuka
and Batista for drinks.

28:13.000 --> 28:17.000
Why don't you bring
the papers and join us?

28:17.000 --> 28:18.542
HOW'S ANGEL DOING?

28:18.542 --> 28:19.917
HOW DO YOU THINK
HE'S DOING?

28:19.917 --> 28:21.917
YOU KNOW, IT'S YOUR FAULT
HE'S IN THIS MESS.

28:21.917 --> 28:23.333
IF YOU HADN'T
FUCKED ELVIRA.

28:23.333 --> 28:26.875
I'M NOT THE BEST BROTHER,
AM I?

28:26.875 --> 28:29.542
DEXTER, ARE YOU
SMOKING SOMETHING?

28:29.542 --> 28:32.041
NO.

28:32.041 --> 28:34.041
I'VE ALWAYS
BEEN CURIOUS TO TRY.

28:34.041 --> 28:35.291
DO YOU HAVE ANY WEED?

28:35.291 --> 28:37.542
OKAY,
NOW I'M REALLY WORRIED.

28:37.542 --> 28:40.000
THERE'S NO NEED
TO WORRY.

28:40.000 --> 28:43.041
I'LL BRING BY THE PAPERS
TOMORROW.

28:43.041 --> 28:45.500
Bye, Deb.

28:45.500 --> 28:46.667
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

28:46.667 --> 28:47.625
IT'S STRANGE.

28:47.625 --> 28:49.208
THIS SHOULD BE DIFFICULT,

28:49.208 --> 28:52.041
BUT A SENSE OF PEACE
IS SETTLING OVER ME.

28:52.041 --> 28:53.834
CALM.

28:56.375 --> 28:58.083
MAYBE IT'S THE MOONLIGHT.

29:05.583 --> 29:07.166
LaGuerta: TOM?

29:07.166 --> 29:09.875
CAN I MEET YOU
OUTSIDE?

29:09.875 --> 29:11.458
OH, SURE.

29:11.458 --> 29:14.875
I'LL CHECK IN
BACK HOME.

29:16.583 --> 29:17.750
I NEED
A PERSONAL DAY.

29:17.750 --> 29:19.250
I HOPE THIS
IS A JOKE.

29:19.250 --> 29:21.083
JUST ONE DAY.

29:21.083 --> 29:22.917
I THINK I CAN PROVE
THAT JAMES IS INNOCENT.

29:22.917 --> 29:24.750
I WAS TALKING TO
A COUPLE OF THE FBI AGENTS

29:24.750 --> 29:26.041
WHO WERE DOWN
IN HAITI --

29:26.041 --> 29:27.000
JESUS CHRIST,
MARIA.

29:27.000 --> 29:29.125
WE ARE IN THE MIDDLE
OF A MANHUNT.

29:29.125 --> 29:31.333
YOU'RE DOWN TWO DETECTIVES,
AND NOW YOU WANT TIME OFF?

29:31.333 --> 29:32.709
THE ANSWER IS NO.

29:32.709 --> 29:34.458
THIS DEPARTMENT CAN'T
SPARE YOU RIGHT NOW.

29:34.458 --> 29:36.792
THIS WASN'T
A REQUEST, TOM.

29:36.792 --> 29:38.750
I WON'T BE HERE
TOMORROW.

29:38.750 --> 29:40.709
I JUST WANTED YOU
TO KNOW THAT.

29:43.792 --> 29:45.041
MMM.

29:45.041 --> 29:47.583
DIABLO.
WHAT IS THIS SHIT,
MASUKA?

29:47.583 --> 29:49.542
HEY, TEQUILA'S
ALL THE SAME.

29:49.542 --> 29:51.417
NOT WHEN IT'S MADE
FROM PUMPKINS.

29:51.417 --> 29:53.750
HEY, WE'RE NOT ALL
IN THE SAME PAY GRADE.

29:53.750 --> 29:56.959
IF I LOSE MY JOB OVER THIS,
BRO, I WON'T HAVE A PAY GRADE.

29:56.959 --> 29:58.667
THAT IS NOT
GONNA HAPPEN.

29:58.667 --> 30:00.667
EVERYONE AT THE STATION
KNOWS YOU'RE INNOCENT.

30:00.667 --> 30:02.000
HOW AM I
GONNA PROVE IT?

30:02.000 --> 30:05.959
HMM? I CAN'T EXPLAIN
THE ROOFIES, THE ROUGH SEX.

30:05.959 --> 30:07.917
THERE WAS ROUGH SEX?
IT WAS HER IDEA.

30:07.917 --> 30:10.625
NOW IT'S MY WORD AGAINST HERS.
I'M SCREWED.

30:10.625 --> 30:13.458
ANGEL, YOU HAVE
GOT TO FIGHT BACK.

30:13.458 --> 30:14.625
DUDE, MORGAN'S RIGHT.

30:14.625 --> 30:17.875
YOU GOT TO MAN UP, GET TOUGH.
LOVE'S A BATTLEFIELD.

30:17.875 --> 30:20.125
OR, IN YOUR CASE,
A RESTRAINING ORDER.

30:20.125 --> 30:21.625
[ CHUCKLES ]

30:21.625 --> 30:23.792
LOOK, I APPRECIATE
YOU GUYS DOING THIS,

30:23.792 --> 30:25.583
BUT YOU DON'T
HAVE TO STAY.

30:25.583 --> 30:28.333
HEY, DOES IT EVER
FLOOR YOU GUYS

30:28.333 --> 30:31.333
THAT WE HAD A KILLER RIGHT UNDER
OUR NOSES THIS WHOLE TIME?

30:31.333 --> 30:34.000
I MEAN, WHO DOESN'T
SEE THAT SHIT?

30:36.166 --> 30:37.750
THAT DIDN'T
COME OUT RIGHT.

30:37.750 --> 30:39.166
IT'S ALL RIGHT.

30:39.166 --> 30:42.458
THAT STUFF DOESN'T
BOTHER ME ANYMORE.

30:42.458 --> 30:43.959
NEXT ROUND'S ON ME.

30:53.166 --> 30:54.959
[ BUZZER ]

31:05.583 --> 31:07.750
DEXTER.

31:07.750 --> 31:10.583
I WAS WONDERING
WHEN YOU'D SHOW UP.

31:10.583 --> 31:12.125
WE NEED TO TALK.

31:12.125 --> 31:13.834
SOUNDS GOOD TO ME.

31:13.834 --> 31:18.333
I'M MAKING COFFEE.
DO YOU WANT ONE?

31:18.333 --> 31:20.542
I'M HERE
TO ASK YOU RESPECTFULLY

31:20.542 --> 31:22.667
TO DROP THE CHARGES
AGAINST ANGEL.

31:22.667 --> 31:24.208
[ SCOFFS ]

31:24.208 --> 31:27.875
DEXTER,
IF ANGEL MOLESTED ME,

31:27.875 --> 31:30.917
AS THE EVIDENCE
SEEMS TO INDICATE,

31:30.917 --> 31:34.250
THEN HE SHOULD
FACE THE CONSEQUENCES,

31:34.250 --> 31:35.709
DON'T YOU THINK?

31:35.709 --> 31:38.917
IT DOESN'T MATTER
WHAT I THINK.

31:38.917 --> 31:41.625
BUT HERE'S
WHAT I KNOW.

31:41.625 --> 31:43.792
AFTER TOMORROW,
I WON'T BE AROUND ANYMORE,

31:43.792 --> 31:45.750
SO THERE'S NO END GAME
IN THIS FOR YOU.

31:45.750 --> 31:48.583
YOU'RE GOING SOMEWHERE?

31:48.583 --> 31:52.083
IT'S LOOKING
MORE AND MORE LIKELY.

31:52.083 --> 31:53.291
WHERE?

31:53.291 --> 31:56.500
ALL THAT MATTERS IS THAT I'LL
BE OUT OF REACH PERMANENTLY.

31:56.500 --> 31:57.875
OH, COME ON,
DEXTER!

31:57.875 --> 31:59.959
TELL ME.
I HAVE A RIGHT TO KNOW.

31:59.959 --> 32:02.917
YOU'RE THE ONE WHO TAUGHT
ME ABOUT ACCEPTING THE
THINGS YOU CAN'T CHANGE.

32:02.917 --> 32:05.208
THIS IS
ONE OF THOSE THINGS.

32:08.208 --> 32:10.041
GOODBYE, LILA.

32:11.208 --> 32:15.083
I DON'T UNDERSTAND
HOW MEN CAN BE SO STUPID.

32:15.083 --> 32:17.709
WELL, NOT ALL  MEN.

32:17.709 --> 32:20.667
YES, EVERY SINGLE
ONE OF YOU.

32:20.667 --> 32:22.625
I MEAN, HOW COULD
DEXTER AND BATISTA

32:22.625 --> 32:24.250
BE SO EASILY DUPED
BY LILA?

32:24.250 --> 32:25.875
I TOOK ONE LOOK AT HER --

32:25.875 --> 32:28.083
I KNEW SHE WAS
A WALKING NIGHTMARE.

32:28.083 --> 32:30.125
THAT'S NOT STUPIDITY.

32:30.125 --> 32:32.250
IT'S SIMPLY IN OUR DNA.

32:32.250 --> 32:34.625
WHEN A PRETTY GIRL SMILES
AND BATS HER EYELASHES,

32:34.625 --> 32:36.041
WE'RE POWERLESS
TO RESIST.

32:38.250 --> 32:40.417
I'M WORRIED
ABOUT BATISTA.

32:40.417 --> 32:42.250
THIS IS SO FUCKED.

32:42.250 --> 32:45.291
THERE'S NO WAY I'M GONNA LET HIM
TAKE THE FALL FOR THIS.

32:45.291 --> 32:46.458
WHAT CAN YOU DO?

32:48.041 --> 32:53.834
WELL...
SPECIAL AGENT LUNDY,

32:53.834 --> 32:55.792
I WAS WONDERING
IF YOU MIGHT ACCESS

32:55.792 --> 32:58.959
THOSE GREAT, BIG
FBI FILES OF YOURS

32:58.959 --> 33:02.458
AND DO A SEARCH
ON MISS LILA TOURNAY.

33:02.458 --> 33:03.792
[ SIGHS ]

33:03.792 --> 33:06.417
YOU SEE?
POWERLESS TO RESIST.

33:06.417 --> 33:08.125
IS ADAMS
GONNA BE PISSED OFF

33:08.125 --> 33:10.625
WHEN HE SEES YOU USED
FBI FILES FOR THIS?

33:10.625 --> 33:12.917
I CERTAINLY HOPE SO.

33:18.125 --> 33:20.959
SHE HAS NO WARRANTS.

33:20.959 --> 33:24.375
NO CRIMINAL RECORD.

33:24.375 --> 33:28.000
NOTHING WITH THE DMV.

33:28.000 --> 33:30.500
[ CLICKING ]

33:30.500 --> 33:33.583
AND NO SOCIAL SECURITY
NUMBER.

33:33.583 --> 33:36.709
WHAT ABOUT VISAS
OR GREEN CARDS OR WHATEVER?

33:36.709 --> 33:39.208
NOTHING.
NO RECORDS.

33:39.208 --> 33:43.667
THAT'S IMPOSSIBLE.
EVERYONE HAS A PAPER TRAIL.

33:43.667 --> 33:46.000
EVERYONE REAL.

33:46.000 --> 33:49.000
THAT SNEAKY BITCH.
SHE'S USING AN ALIAS.

33:49.000 --> 33:51.166
THAT WOULD BE
MY GUESS.

33:51.166 --> 33:54.083
WELL, HOW DO I FIND OUT
LILA'S REAL NAME?

33:54.083 --> 33:57.083
I THINK YOU KNOW
THE ANSWER TO THAT.

33:57.083 --> 33:59.667
CUT OFF HER HEAD,
LOOK FOR A LABEL.

33:59.667 --> 34:00.875
[ LAUGHS ]

34:00.875 --> 34:04.583
THERE'S PROBABLY
AN EASIER WAY.

34:09.542 --> 34:11.333
[ GROANS ]

34:12.917 --> 34:14.458
YOU GOT
SOMETHING SMALLER?

34:14.458 --> 34:16.959
THE LAST TIME LILA
WAS IN MY APARTMENT,

34:16.959 --> 34:18.667
SHE MICROWAVED
SOME POPCORN.

34:18.667 --> 34:21.208
THERE'S DEFINITELY
GONNA BE PRINTS ON THIS.

34:22.959 --> 34:24.375
ALL RIGHT, GOT IT.

34:24.375 --> 34:27.208
NEXT TIME,
MAKE HER A CUP OF TEA.

34:35.083 --> 34:37.333
THIS IS MARLENE
FROM ACCOUNTING.

34:37.333 --> 34:39.166
HI, MARLENE
FROM ACCOUNTING.

34:39.166 --> 34:41.208
SHE'S ALSO
A NOTARY PUBLIC.

34:41.208 --> 34:42.375
GOOD FOR YOU.

34:42.375 --> 34:44.959
I MET WITH
A LAWYER YESTERDAY,

34:44.959 --> 34:46.417
AND HE HELPED ME
PREPARE A LIVING TRUST

34:46.417 --> 34:48.000
THAT GIVES YOU CONTROL
OFF ALL MY ASSETS

34:48.000 --> 34:53.458
IN THE EVENT OF MY DEATH
OR CERTAIN OTHER SITUATIONS.

34:53.458 --> 34:56.083
OH, GOD. GO AWAY.
THIS IS CREEPY.

34:56.083 --> 34:58.709
MY FINANCIAL PLANNER SAID
A GUY MY AGE SHOULD HAVE A WILL.

34:58.709 --> 34:59.750
IT'S JUST A PRECAUTION.

34:59.750 --> 35:01.625
WE'RE ALL GOING
TO DIE EVENTUALLY.

35:04.417 --> 35:05.583
[ CHUCKLES ]

35:05.583 --> 35:07.875
OKAY. YEAH.

35:07.875 --> 35:10.291
IS THIS WHY YOU WERE
ACTING SO WEIRD LAST NIGHT?

35:10.291 --> 35:13.125
YEAH, PROBABLY.

35:13.125 --> 35:15.458
SIGN HERE AND HERE,
AND I'LL NEED TO SEE AN I.D.

35:15.458 --> 35:18.208
FINE.

35:18.208 --> 35:20.750
THANKS FOR SHOWING UP LAST NIGHT
TO SUPPORT BATISTA.

35:20.750 --> 35:22.041
I AM SUPPORTING
BATISTA.

35:22.041 --> 35:24.166
I STOPPED BY LILA'S
THIS MORNING.

35:24.166 --> 35:25.291
AND?

35:25.291 --> 35:26.500
AND I TALKED
TO HER.

35:26.500 --> 35:28.542
I DON'T THINK
SHE'S GONNA BE A PROBLEM.

35:28.542 --> 35:32.542
YEAH, 'CAUSE SHE CERTAINLY
HASN'T BEEN ONE SO FAR.

35:32.542 --> 35:33.625
HEY, I'M FREE TONIGHT.

35:33.625 --> 35:36.000
YOU WANT TO STOP BY,
I'LL PICK UP SOME BEERS,

35:36.000 --> 35:37.792
THROW ON
A COUPLE OF STEAKS?

35:37.792 --> 35:40.125
THERE'S SOMETHING
I WANT TO TALK TO YOU ABOUT.

35:40.125 --> 35:42.625
SURE.
SOUNDS GOOD.

35:42.625 --> 35:44.625
SO, WHAT AM I GETTING?

35:44.625 --> 35:47.125
I COULD USE A NEW TV.

35:52.834 --> 35:54.959
OKAY.
BUT THAT'S THE ONE.

35:54.959 --> 35:56.291
Lundy:
Lundy here.

35:56.291 --> 35:58.417
OH, SPECIAL AGENT LUNDY.

35:58.417 --> 36:00.959
IT'S LIEUTENANT LaGUERTA.
I'M CALLING YOU FROM HAITI.

36:00.959 --> 36:03.000
LOVELY
THIS TIME OF YEAR.

36:03.000 --> 36:04.750
I UNDERSTAND THAT
I'M NOT YOUR FAVORITE PERSON

36:04.750 --> 36:08.125
IN THE STATION RIGHT NOW,
BUT I REALLY NEED YOUR HELP.

36:08.125 --> 36:10.583
How so?

36:10.583 --> 36:11.875
I JUST MET WITH LEONES,

36:11.875 --> 36:13.709
THE TRAVEL AGENT
THAT DOAKES SAW.

36:13.709 --> 36:15.333
THERE'S
NOTHING NEW THERE.

36:15.333 --> 36:17.417
I HAD TWO AGENTS
QUESTION HIM FOR HOURS.

36:17.417 --> 36:20.125
YET HE NEVER TOLD THEM
ABOUT THE BLOOD SLIDES.

36:20.125 --> 36:22.375
What does he know
about the blood slides?

36:22.375 --> 36:25.709
Doakes was looking for a lab
to have them analyzed.

36:25.709 --> 36:26.709
WHY?

36:26.709 --> 36:28.166
I DON'T KNOW WHY.

36:28.166 --> 36:30.208
If he's our killer, he'd be
keeping them for trophies.

36:30.208 --> 36:31.917
HE'D HAVE NO REASON
TO HAVE THEM ANALYZED.

36:31.917 --> 36:34.583
AND I ALSO HAVE A LIST
OF SPECIAL-OPS MISSIONS

36:34.583 --> 36:37.333
THAT LEONES PERSONALLY
KNOWS DOAKES TOOK PART IN.

36:37.333 --> 36:40.083
NOW, TWO OF THEM DIRECTLY
CONFLICT WITH MURDERS

36:40.083 --> 36:43.458
WE KNOW TO HAVE BEEN COMMITTED
BY THE BAY HARBOR BUTCHER.

36:43.458 --> 36:45.750
I'M NOT SURE LEONES
IS OUR MOST RELIABLE WITNESS.

36:45.750 --> 36:50.375
No, but it's worth
looking into, isn't it?

36:51.917 --> 36:54.041
YES.
YES, IT IS.

36:54.041 --> 36:55.875
YES! OKAY.

36:55.875 --> 37:01.875
FOR STARTERS, WHY DON'T YOU
BRIEF ME ON BOTH THOSE MISSIONS?

37:01.875 --> 37:04.667
GIVE ME
ALL THE DETAILS.

37:06.709 --> 37:08.750
Dexter: COME ON, CODY.
UP AND OVER.

37:08.750 --> 37:10.041
OKAY. GREAT.

37:10.041 --> 37:12.750
OKAY, ASTOR.
UP AND OVER.

37:12.750 --> 37:15.250
THERE WE GO.

37:17.166 --> 37:19.375
WATCH YOUR STEP.

37:33.083 --> 37:37.125
LOOK,
THERE'S A PELICAN.

37:37.125 --> 37:39.417
WHAT'S THAT?

38:16.750 --> 38:22.125
Female voice: WELCOME TO
THE GPS 3000 TELETRACKER.

38:22.125 --> 38:24.583
PREVIOUS DESTINATIONS.

38:33.917 --> 38:37.750
Dexter:
FOR SO LONG MY BOAT HAS BEEN
A TOOL OF MY DARK TRADE --

38:37.750 --> 38:39.250
A GRAVEYARD TRANSPORT.

38:39.250 --> 38:42.333
I'D ALMOST FORGOTTEN IT COULD
DOUBLE AS A PLEASURE CRAFT.

38:42.333 --> 38:44.792
NOW, THE THING IS,
IF YOU CATCH A WHALE,

38:44.792 --> 38:47.125
WE'RE PROBABLY GONNA
HAVE TO PUT IT BACK.

38:47.125 --> 38:49.583
IF IT'S A BABY,
WE COULD PUT IT IN THE BATHTUB.

38:49.583 --> 38:51.959
I'M NOT GONNA TAKE A BATH
WITH A WHALE.

38:51.959 --> 38:54.291
I KNOW, THEY ALWAYS
USE UP ALL THE SOAP.

38:56.542 --> 38:58.333
[ CHUCKLES ]

39:02.750 --> 39:04.458
IT'S PEACEFUL
OUT HERE.

39:11.667 --> 39:14.667
RITA, I'VE NEVER BEEN
A VERY GOOD BOYFRIEND.

39:14.667 --> 39:17.959
I WOULDN'T SAY THAT.

39:19.583 --> 39:23.208
I JUST NEED YOU TO KNOW
THAT YOU AND THE KIDS

39:23.208 --> 39:26.500
ARE VERY IMPORTANT
TO ME.

39:26.500 --> 39:30.166
NO MATTER WHAT HAPPENS,
I WANT YOU TO ALWAYS KNOW THAT.

39:32.542 --> 39:34.542
OKAY, DEXTER.

39:37.291 --> 39:40.083
HEY, EVERYTHING'S
ALL RIGHT.

39:40.083 --> 39:42.125
OKAY?

39:42.125 --> 39:45.500
I JUST -- I JUST NEED
TO TAKE THINGS SLOW.

39:46.834 --> 39:47.792
[ CHUCKLES ]

39:47.792 --> 39:50.250
OH, I HAVE A GIFT
FOR YOU.

39:50.250 --> 39:52.375
DEXTER, YOU DON'T NEED
TO BRING ME GIFTS.

39:52.375 --> 39:53.917
I WANT YOU
TO HAVE THIS.

39:53.917 --> 39:55.875
IT'S THE PINK SLIP
TO THE MINI-VAN.

39:55.875 --> 39:57.417
DEXTER, I TOLD YOU
EVERYTHING'S OKAY.

39:57.417 --> 39:59.041
YOU DON'T --

39:59.041 --> 40:01.375
PLEASE, I WANT YOU TO HAVE IT
FOR THE KIDS.

40:01.375 --> 40:04.083
IT'LL KEEP THEM SAFER
THAN A BROKEN-DOWN CONVERTIBLE.

40:05.917 --> 40:08.625
THANK YOU.

40:08.625 --> 40:10.166
VERY GENEROUS.

40:10.166 --> 40:13.542
YOU'RE WELCOME.

40:13.542 --> 40:17.750
I KNOW I'VE BEEN
TAKING THINGS SLOW WITH US,

40:17.750 --> 40:21.417
BUT IT'S NOT BECAUSE
I DON'T HAVE FEELINGS FOR YOU.

40:21.417 --> 40:24.250
IT'S MORE LIKE
I HAVE TOO MANY FEELINGS,

40:24.250 --> 40:27.250
AND I JUST WANT TO MAKE SURE
TO GET IT RIGHT.

40:29.208 --> 40:31.375
ME TOO.

40:41.583 --> 40:45.333
THAT'S NOT EXACTLY
TAKING IT SLOW.

40:45.333 --> 40:48.625
SORRY. I'LL NEVER
DO THAT AGAIN.

40:48.625 --> 40:51.125
WELL, DON'T SAY NEVER.

40:54.875 --> 40:56.750
[ SIGHS ]

41:00.250 --> 41:02.000
I WAS JUST
LOOKING FOR YOU.

41:02.000 --> 41:04.000
THE BOYS LOOKED
AT LILA'S PRINTS.

41:04.000 --> 41:05.250
WE HIT THE JACKPOT.

41:05.250 --> 41:06.375
OH?

41:06.375 --> 41:08.125
TURNS OUT HER REAL NAME
IS LILA WEST.

41:08.125 --> 41:09.417
I RAN HER PRINTS
THROUGH THE AFIS,

41:09.417 --> 41:10.583
WHICH IS
TIED TO I.C.E.

41:10.583 --> 41:14.125
GET THIS -- HER VISA EXPIRED
TWO YEARS AGO.

41:14.125 --> 41:15.291
BAD GIRL.

41:15.291 --> 41:17.166
I CAN HAVE HER
DEPORTED.

41:17.166 --> 41:19.333
NOT AS EASY
AS IT SOUNDS.

41:19.333 --> 41:22.333
MIAMI IS SWAMPED
WITH CRIMINAL IMMIGRANTS,

41:22.333 --> 41:24.750
REFUGEES FROM
THIRD-WORLD COUNTRIES.

41:24.750 --> 41:27.125
THEY'LL TAKE PRIORITY
OVER SOME BRITISH GIRL.

41:27.125 --> 41:28.625
THEN I'LL DEPORT HER
MYSELF.

41:28.625 --> 41:30.208
WE GOT HIM.

41:30.208 --> 41:31.291
DOAKES?

41:31.291 --> 41:33.959
TALKED TO A PARK-SERVICE MANAGER
IN THE EVERGLADES

41:33.959 --> 41:37.166
WHO REMEMBERS GIVING SERGEANT
DOAKES DIRECTIONS FIVE DAYS AGO.

41:37.166 --> 41:39.125
SO YOU HAVE A TIP --
NOT DOAKES.

41:39.125 --> 41:42.250
THE PARK MANAGER SAID OUR TARGET
WAS HEADED INTO THE EVERGLADES

41:42.250 --> 41:43.709
15 MILES NORTH
OF SUNDAY BAY.

41:43.709 --> 41:46.959
WE WILL HAVE THE SON OF A BITCH
IN HANDCUFFS IN 24 HOURS.

41:46.959 --> 41:50.667
I'D LIKE TO URGE STRONG CAUTION
IN APPREHENDING THE SUSPECT.

41:50.667 --> 41:52.875
I'M LOOKING INTO NEW INFORMATION
THAT MIGHT COME INTO PLAY --

41:52.875 --> 41:55.041
YEAH, I GOT YOUR E-MAIL
ABOUT LEONES.

41:55.041 --> 41:57.333
THE MAN WILL SAY ANYTHING
FOR A DOLLAR.

41:57.333 --> 41:59.000
I AGREE WE HAVE TO BE
CIRCUMSPECT ABOUT THIS,

41:59.000 --> 42:01.000
WHICH IS EXACTLY
WHY I'D LIKE SOME TIME.

42:01.000 --> 42:03.417
SHOW A LITTLE GUTS,
FOR CHRIST'S SAKES.

42:03.417 --> 42:05.458
WHY DON'T YOU
SHOW A LITTLE RESPECT?

42:05.458 --> 42:07.375
YOU WOULDN'T BE CLOSING IN
ON A SUSPECT RIGHT NOW

42:07.375 --> 42:10.000
IF IT WASN'T FOR
THE WORK OF THIS MAN.

42:10.000 --> 42:11.458
[ LAUGHS ]

42:11.458 --> 42:14.291
YOU KNOW, AS MUCH AS I ENJOY
HEARING FROM THE LOCAL TALENT,

42:14.291 --> 42:16.500
I'M REALLY RATHER BUSY
RIGHT NOW.

42:19.750 --> 42:21.375
WELL, I'M GUESSING
YOU DON'T NEED ME

42:21.375 --> 42:22.834
TO FIGHT YOUR BATTLES
ANYMORE.

42:22.834 --> 42:24.834
YEAH, WELL, MAYBE
YOU NEED ME TO FIGHT YOURS.

42:24.834 --> 42:27.041
OOH.
AREN'T YOU A TOUGH ONE?

42:27.041 --> 42:28.834
I'M JUST WARMING UP.

42:40.917 --> 42:44.083
WOW. I THOUGHT
I LIVED IN A SHIT CAN.

42:44.083 --> 42:48.667
OFFICER MORGAN, HAVE YOU COME
TO INQUIRE ABOUT MY WELFARE?

42:48.667 --> 42:51.083
I WANT YOU
TO LEAVE MIAMI TONIGHT.

42:51.083 --> 42:52.583
DON'T EVER COME BACK.

42:52.583 --> 42:55.542
DON'T EVER CONTACT ANGEL
OR DEXTER AGAIN.

42:57.375 --> 43:01.041
AND, UM, WHY WOULD I
LISTEN TO YOU?

43:01.041 --> 43:02.208
'CAUSE I'M A COP.

43:02.208 --> 43:04.500
AND YOU'RE HERE
ON AN EXPIRED VISA.

43:07.083 --> 43:08.291
I KNOW YOUR REAL NAME,

43:08.291 --> 43:10.083
AND I'VE CONTACTED
IMMIGRATION.

43:10.083 --> 43:12.125
OFFICERS WILL BE HERE
ANY DAY NOW.

43:12.125 --> 43:14.417
THEY'LL ARREST YOU
AND DEPORT YOU,

43:14.417 --> 43:16.500
AND IT WILL NOT
BE PRETTY.

43:16.500 --> 43:17.667
IF THIS IS TRUE,

43:17.667 --> 43:19.792
WHY ARE YOU
TELLING ME THIS?

43:19.792 --> 43:22.458
BECAUSE I WANT YOU
THE FUCK OUT OF HERE NOW.

43:22.458 --> 43:24.166
WHETHER YOU LEAVE
ON YOUR OWN

43:24.166 --> 43:26.542
OR IMMIGRATION HAULS
YOUR SORRY ASS AWAY,

43:26.542 --> 43:27.667
I DON'T GIVE A SHIT.

43:27.667 --> 43:30.083
BUT I DON'T WANT TO GIVE YOU
ONE MORE DAY

43:30.083 --> 43:33.125
TO FUCK WITH THE PEOPLE
I CARE ABOUT.

43:33.125 --> 43:34.583
I WANT YOU GONE.

43:34.583 --> 43:35.500
TONIGHT.

43:35.500 --> 43:38.041
YOU DON'T WANT TO
DO THIS.

43:38.041 --> 43:41.500
IT'S DONE.

43:41.500 --> 43:43.291
TONIGHT.

44:09.083 --> 44:10.667
[ BEEP ]

44:10.667 --> 44:13.000
Female voice: WELCOME.
PREVIOUS DESTINATION.

44:13.000 --> 44:14.250
STARTING ROUTE GUIDANCE.

44:14.250 --> 44:17.166
LEFT TURN AHEAD.

44:25.542 --> 44:28.333
Dexter: I KEEP EXPECTING
TO COME TO MY SENSES,

44:28.333 --> 44:32.875
BUT THE PRESSURE IS LIFTING
WITH EACH STEP I TAKE.

44:32.875 --> 44:36.500
I'VE SPENT A LIFETIME
KEEPING UP MY GUARD,

44:36.500 --> 44:39.041
WATCHING MY BACK,
WEARING MY MASK.

44:39.041 --> 44:44.208
RELIEF WAS NEVER IN SIGHT
UNTIL NOW.

44:44.208 --> 44:45.542
[ SIZZLING ]

44:45.542 --> 44:49.667
IF ANYONE DESERVES TO TAKE
ME INTO CUSTODY, IT'S DEB.

44:49.667 --> 44:52.208
BUT HOW DO I TELL HER
WHAT I AM?

45:06.834 --> 45:09.166
DEB,
I'M THE BAY HARBOR BUTCHER.

45:13.583 --> 45:15.959
[ COUGHING ]

45:15.959 --> 45:17.500
DEB,
I'M THE BAY HARBOR BUTCHER.

45:17.500 --> 45:18.542
ON THE GROUND.

45:18.542 --> 45:20.834
DOWN ON THE GROUND,
MOTHERFUCKER.

45:20.834 --> 45:24.041
IT'S ME.
I'M THE BAY HARBOR BUTCHER.

45:24.041 --> 45:27.125
[ Sobbing ]
NO, NO, NO, NO, NO.

45:27.125 --> 45:29.583
I'M HIM -- THE BUTCHER.

45:32.375 --> 45:36.000
THIS ISN'T GOING TO BE EASY.

45:36.000 --> 45:37.709
[ DOOR OPENS ]

45:39.041 --> 45:43.458
I BROUGHT EXTRA BEER.
WE'RE GETTING DRUNK.

45:43.458 --> 45:45.500
FINE WITH ME.

45:50.208 --> 45:53.375
WHAT'S THE OCCASION?

45:53.375 --> 45:58.041
I RAN LILA
OUT OF TOWN TODAY.

45:58.041 --> 45:59.333
REALLY?
YEAH.

45:59.333 --> 46:01.375
TURNS OUT
SHE'S HERE ILLEGALLY.

46:01.375 --> 46:03.375
YOU SHOULD HAVE
SEEN ME, DEX.

46:03.375 --> 46:05.959
I WAS LIKE
AN OLD-WEST SHERIFF.

46:10.125 --> 46:13.583
YOU'RE REALLY
FEELING GOOD.

46:14.583 --> 46:16.625
FUCK, YEAH.

46:16.625 --> 46:18.458
I GOT TO SAY,
GREAT TIMING, DEX,

46:18.458 --> 46:20.041
GETTING TOGETHER TONIGHT.

46:20.041 --> 46:22.583
THE LAST FEW MONTHS,
I WAS STARTING TO FEEL LIKE

46:22.583 --> 46:24.333
I HAD MY HEAD
PRETTY FAR UP MY ASS.

46:24.333 --> 46:26.667
NO ONE BLAMES YOU.

46:26.667 --> 46:30.458
YOUR WORLD
WAS TURNED UPSIDE DOWN.

46:30.458 --> 46:32.583
LIKE MINE IS NOW.

46:32.583 --> 46:35.458
FOR THE FIRST TIME SINCE
THAT ICE-TRUCK KILLER SHIT,

46:35.458 --> 46:37.458
I FEEL LIKE I'M BACK.

46:37.458 --> 46:40.417
NEW AND IMPROVED, EVEN.

46:50.625 --> 46:55.250
WHEN ALL THAT STUFF
WAS HAPPENING --

46:55.250 --> 46:57.250
WITH RUDY, I MEAN...

47:02.291 --> 47:05.583
...DID YOU EVER CONSIDER
DOING SOMETHING DRASTIC?

47:08.917 --> 47:10.333
ARE YOU KIDDING?

47:12.667 --> 47:16.792
ALL KINDS OF FUCKED-UP SHIT
RAN THROUGH MY HEAD.

47:16.792 --> 47:18.959
THANK GOD I HAD YOU.

47:18.959 --> 47:21.000
REALLY?

47:21.000 --> 47:22.166
YEAH.

47:22.166 --> 47:24.333
EVERY TIME I STARTED
TO SPIN OUT OF CONTROL,

47:24.333 --> 47:26.041
I HAD YOU TO GRAB ONTO.

47:26.041 --> 47:30.166
HELL, YOU LET ME LIVE HERE
PRACTICALLY FOREVER.

47:30.166 --> 47:31.500
IT WAS TOUGH, THOUGH.

47:31.500 --> 47:33.500
I'D HAVE DONE
ALMOST ANYTHING

47:33.500 --> 47:36.291
TO GET OUT FROM UNDER
THE WEIGHT OF IT ALL.

47:38.542 --> 47:43.125
HOW'D YOU FINALLY DO IT?

47:44.750 --> 47:50.208
I JUST --
JUST SAW THROUGH IT.

47:50.208 --> 47:52.166
YOU KNOW?

47:52.166 --> 47:56.000
YOU DECIDE WHO YOU ARE,
WHO YOU WANT TO BE...

47:58.792 --> 48:04.667
...AND YOU HOLD ONTO THAT
AND RIDE IT OUT.

48:11.583 --> 48:14.250
LIKE AN OLD-WEST SHERIFF.

48:20.709 --> 48:25.250
BROTHER, THIS IS WORTH
LIVING FOR.

48:28.291 --> 48:30.208
RIGHT?

48:30.208 --> 48:32.375
[ CHUCKLES ]

48:37.333 --> 48:40.083
YOU ARE ABSOLUTELY RIGHT.

48:40.083 --> 48:42.041
HEY, WHAT DID YOU WANT TO
TALK TO ME ABOUT, ANYWAY?

48:43.917 --> 48:48.542
OH...NOTHING.

48:50.750 --> 48:52.917
NOTHING AT ALL.

48:57.709 --> 49:01.000
SO, THIS IS ME,
RIDING IT OUT.

49:01.000 --> 49:04.583
HARRY MAY HAVE REJECTED ME,
BUT DEB CLEARLY BELIEVES IN ME,

49:04.583 --> 49:06.083
SO WHY SHOULDN'T I?

49:06.083 --> 49:07.834
I'M NOT TURNING MYSELF IN.

49:07.834 --> 49:10.000
THIS ISN'T HARRY'S LIFE.

49:10.000 --> 49:11.417
IT'S MINE.

49:11.417 --> 49:15.041
I MADE A PLAN TO FRAME DOAKES,
AND I'M GOING TO STICK WITH IT.

49:15.041 --> 49:20.083
[ CELLPHONE RINGS ]

49:20.083 --> 49:22.375
MORGAN.

49:22.375 --> 49:25.792
NO SHIT?

49:25.792 --> 49:28.333
OKAY.
OKAY, I'M ON THE WAY.

49:28.333 --> 49:31.667
THEY FOUND DOAKES'
FUCKING RENTAL CAR.

49:31.667 --> 49:33.875
THEY FOUND -- REALLY?

49:33.875 --> 49:35.667
HIS CAR?

49:35.667 --> 49:36.834
DID THEY FIND DOAKES?

49:36.834 --> 49:38.959
